citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 11:30 AM on
27DECEMBER2022. Inspector arrival to premise at 1130. Phoned licensee at primary contact number, no answer,
voicemail box full. Texted licensee at same number and left message. Knocked on front door of residence, no answer.
Inspector departure from premise at 1207.
End Section
